sprain. Also missing practice Monday were fullback Greg Comella
(back), running back Omar Bacon (hamstring), defensive tackle Ryan
Hale (shoulder), safety Tawambi Settles (shoulder), defensive end
Jeremiah Parker (stinger), guard Mike Rosenthal (shoulder) and
